i wrote POS about the negative voice thats in your head and trying to silence or runaway from it. the high pitched chorus is supposed to represent the voice itself and the shift to a unaltered tone at the end yelling “STFU” represents the trying to silence it, while the verses are all storytelling based. it’s something i’ve struggled with my whole life, overcoming the dark thoughts, and i think it’s a issue we all deal with to one extent or the other. it can be the hardest thing to shine light on the darkest places within ourselves but it’s only then that we can air them out and change for the better… POS out now🖤luv yall
